cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a framework for generating and manipulating face images with desired attributes, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also utilizes GAN framework, which is a popular deep learning technique, and hence can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with image generation and editing, which can be categorized under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
